<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Help & Support | Dekrof</title>
     <%- include('./partials/headerlinks')%>
</head>

<body class="bg-zinc-900 text-white">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-white">
        <div class="p-2">
            <a href="/home" class="text-blue-500 font-bold">return to previous page</a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-zinc-700 rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12">

            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold ">
                Help & Support
            </h1>

            <p class="mt-3 ">
                If you have any questions, encounter a bug, or would like to suggest
                a new feature, feel free to contact me using the information below.
            </p>


            <section class="mt-12">

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold  border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-3">
                    Account Support
                </h2>

                <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5">

                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-5">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold ">
                            Password Reset
                        </h3>

                        <p class="mt-2 ">
                            If you are unable to access your account or need to reset your
                            password, please contact the administrator. Include your
                            registered username and explain the issue. For security
                            reasons, you may be asked to verify your identity before any
                            changes are made.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-5">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold ">
                            Report a User
                        </h3>

                        <p class="mt-2 ">
                            If you encounter spam, harassment, impersonation, abusive
                            behavior, or any activity that violates the community
                            guidelines, please report the user by contacting the
                            administrator.
                        </p>

                        <p class="mt-3 ">
                            Your report should include:
                        </p>

                        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ">
                            <li>Username of the reported account.</li>
                            <li>Description of the incident.</li>
                            <li>Date and time (if known).</li>
                            <li>Screenshots or other supporting evidence.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </section>

            <section class="mt-12">

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold  border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-3">
                    Reporting an Issue
                </h2>
                <p class="mt-5 ">
                    To help resolve issues quickly, please include the following
                    information:
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-4 list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ">
                    <li>A clear description of the issue.</li>
                    <li>Steps to reproduce it.</li>
                    <li>Screenshots or screen recordings (if applicable).</li>
                    <li>Your browser and operating system.</li>
                </ul>

            </section>
            <section class="mt-10">

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold  border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-3">
                    Developer Information
                </h2>

                <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">

                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Developer</p>
                        <p class="font-medium">
                            Satyam Chauhan
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <p class="text-sm ">Email</p>
                        <a href="mailto:satyamchauhan9656@gmail.com"
                           class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
                            satyamchauhan9656@gmail.com
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <p class="text-sm ">GitHub</p>
                        <a href="https://github.com/satyam088"
                           target="_blank"
                           class="text-blue-600 hover:underline break-all">
                            https://github.com/satyam088
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border rounded-lg p-4">
                        <p class="text-sm ">LinkedIn</p>
                        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/satyam088"
                           target="_blank"
                           class="text-blue-600 hover:underline break-all">
                            https://linkedin.com/in/satyam088
                        </a>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="mt-12">

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold  border-l-4 border-blue-600 pl-3">
                    Project Repository
                </h2>

                <p class="mt-5 ">
                    The complete source code for <strong>Dekrof</strong> is available
                    on GitHub. Feel free to explore the project, report issues, or
                    contribute through pull requests.
                </p>

                <a href="https://github.com/Satyam088/dekrof"
                   target="_blank"
                   class="inline-block mt-5 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-zinc-500 text-white hover:bg-black transition">
                    View GitHub Repository
                </a>

            </section>

            <div class="mt-12 border-t pt-6 text-center text-sm">
                © 2026 Dekrof. All Rights Reserved.
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>